readme_content = """\
# AI Chatbot

This project is an AI chatbot powered by OpenAI's GPT-3.5-turbo model. The chatbot is implemented as a Flask application and uses a Tkinter interface for user interaction.

## Requirements

- Python 3.8 or higher
- Flask 2.0.1
- OpenAI
- NLTK
- Requests 2.25.1

You can install these packages using pip:

\`\`\`
pip install -r requirements.txt
\`\`\`

## Running the Application

To run the application, first set your OpenAI API key as an environment variable:

\`\`\`
export OPENAI_API_KEY=your_api_key
\`\`\`

Then, start the Flask server:

\`\`\`
python app.py
\`\`\`

Finally, run the Tkinter interface:

\`\`\`
python main.py
\`\`\`

## Usage

Type your message into the entry box and press Enter to send it. The chatbot's response will be displayed above the entry box.

## License

This project is licensed under the terms of the MIT license.
"""
